{"title":"hexo博客添加live2d看板娘","date":"2020-05-08T05:12:15.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年5月8日","L":"2020/05/08","MM-DD":"05-08"},"link":"posts/2805db8d","comments":true,"categories":["博客"],"updated":"2020-06-08T01:51:40.886Z","content":"<h1 id=\"下载安装\">下载安装<a href=\"#下载安装\" title=\"下载安装\"></a></h1><p>检测npm版本是否最新</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote>\n<p>npm更新方法:</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">nmp install npm@latest -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id=\"安装hexo-helper-live2d\">安装hexo-helper-live2d<a href=\"#安装hexo-helper-live2d\" title=\"安装hexo-helper-live2d\"></a></h1><p>进入<code>hexo</code>目录下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install –save hexo-helper-lived</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开<code>hexo</code>目录下的<code>_config.yml</code>的配置文件</p>\n<h1 id=\"配置\">配置<a href=\"#配置\" title=\"配置\"></a></h1><blockquote>\n<p>将以下代码添加到站点配置文件末尾</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">  # Live2D</span><br><span class=\"line\">## https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;EYHN&#x2F;hexo-helper-live2d</span><br><span class=\"line\">live2d:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  enable: true</span><br><span class=\"line\">  # scriptFrom: jsdelivr # jsdelivr CDN</span><br><span class=\"line\">  # scriptFrom: unpkg # unpkg CDN</span><br><span class=\"line\">  # scriptFrom: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;npm&#x2F;live2d-widget@3.x&#x2F;lib&#x2F;L2Dwidget.min.js # 你的自定义 url</span><br><span class=\"line\">  # use: wanko # 博客根目录&#x2F;live2d_models&#x2F; 下的目录名</span><br><span class=\"line\">  # use: .&#x2F;wives&#x2F;wanko # 相对于博客根目录的路径</span><br><span class=\"line\">  # use: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;npm&#x2F;live2d-widget-model-wanko@1.0.5&#x2F;assets&#x2F;wanko.model.json # 你的自定义 url</span><br><span class=\"line\">  # enable: false</span><br><span class=\"line\">  scriptFrom: local # 默认</span><br><span class=\"line\">  pluginRootPath: live2dw&#x2F; # 插件在站点上的根目录(相对路径)</span><br><span class=\"line\">  pluginJsPath: lib&#x2F; # 脚本文件相对与插件根目录路径</span><br><span class=\"line\">  pluginModelPath: assets&#x2F; # 模型文件相对与插件根目录路径</span><br><span class=\"line\">  model:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    use: live2d-widget-model-ni-j # npm-module package name</span><br><span class=\"line\">    scale: 1</span><br><span class=\"line\">    hHeadPos: 0.5</span><br><span class=\"line\">    vHeadPos: 0.618</span><br><span class=\"line\">  display:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    superSample: 2</span><br><span class=\"line\">    width: 150</span><br><span class=\"line\">    height: 300</span><br><span class=\"line\">    position: left</span><br><span class=\"line\">    hOffset: 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">    vOffset: -50</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mobile:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    show: true</span><br><span class=\"line\">    scale: 0.5</span><br><span class=\"line\">  react:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    opacityDefault: 0.7</span><br><span class=\"line\">    opacityOnHover: 0.2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id=\"下载模型动画\">下载模型动画<a href=\"#下载模型动画\" title=\"下载模型动画\"></a></h1><p><a href=\"https://huaji8.top/post/live2d-plugin-2.0/\" target=\"_blank\">后宫预览点这里</a><br><a href=\"https://github.com/xiazeyu/live2d-widget-models\" target=\"_blank\">选择你的后宫</a><br>看好了默默记下小姐姐的名字,<strong>初音</strong>的模型名字:ni-j<br>博客中都是按照<code>ni-j</code>操作</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install –save live2d-widget-model-ni-j</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote>\n<p>此时<strong>初音</strong>模型已经下载完毕</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">model:</span><br><span class=\"line\">   use: live2d-widget-model-ni-j # 将&#96;ni-j&#96;替换成其他包名,即可替换不同模型人物.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id=\"资源\">资源<a href=\"#资源\" title=\"资源\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[github源码和中文操作指南][3]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id=\"重新加载博客\">重新加载博客<a href=\"#重新加载博客\" title=\"重新加载博客\"></a></h1><blockquote>\n<p>hexo clean<br>hexo g<br>打开浏览器看看你的初音吧</p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"Butterfly主题更新总结","link":"posts/d1a5291c"},"next":{"title":"hexo博客开启pwa","link":"posts/805d5d89"},"plink":"https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/2805db8d/","toc":[{"id":"下载安装","title":"下载安装","index":"1"},{"id":"安装hexo-helper-live2d","title":"安装hexo-helper-live2d","index":"2"},{"id":"配置","title":"配置","index":"3"},{"id":"下载模型动画","title":"下载模型动画","index":"4"},{"id":"资源","title":"资源","index":"5"},{"id":"重新加载博客","title":"重新加载博客","index":"6"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"DxSummer","link":"<a href=\"https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/2805db8d/\" title=\"hexo博客添加live2d看板娘\">https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/2805db8d/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"2020年5月8日","updated":"2020年6月8日"}}